    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klaufsajt juhs/ kas juhs tchs ne warr dsirdeht/ kam ne-\ntahfu eſtat/ ko es efimu darrijs/\nfaprohtama WalloDa irr/ ko ne\nun kas juhs twru eſfat/ atsib-\nwarr faprast.\nſteet mannu Warru."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tce Grehzineeki Zianâ\nirr iſbihjajufchees/ Drebbetcha-\nnairr teem Blehdneefkeem usgah-\njusi/ (tee fatka:) Kas irr muhfu\nStarpâ/ kas pee weena aprih-\njama llaguns warr dsihwoht?\nKas irr muhfu Starpâ/ kas pee\nmuhſchigahm Swelmehim dsih-\nwoht warr?"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas eekſch Taifnibas stat-\nga/ un runna kas teefi irr. Kas\nnetaisnus Nopeluns eenibſt/ kas\nfawas Rohkas ſchfibſtas turr no\nDahwann Reimchanas. Kas\nfawn Anti atebahſch no Affins-\nGrehku Klauſitchanas/ kas fa-\nwas Azzis aisdarra/ ka tahs to\nLaunu ne neluhko."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas pats dsihwohs Aug-\nftiba/ to Akminna-Ralnu Stip-\nrumi buhs winnam par augstu\nPatwerunu. Winnam buhs\nfawa Maife/ winna Uhdens\nbuhs winnam teefchain."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawas Azzis redſehs to\nRehninu sawâ Skatſtuma. Tahs\nredſehs ka ta Semme taps is-\nplattita."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawa Sirde atminnehs\nto Baillibu/un tizzibs: Kur irr\ntas Raſtu-Mahzitajs? Kur irr\ntas Runnas-Kungs? Kur irr\ntas Kanzleris?"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tobs ſtiprus Laudis tu\nwairs ne redſeft/ tohs Laudis/\nkam ſweſchas Mehles irr/ ka"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi Zianu/ to Pilſ-\nfahtu muhfas Sa-eefchanas/ ta-\nwas Azzis redſehs Jeruſaleimi\nweenu drohſchu Mahjas-Weetu/\nweenu Dsihwokli/ kas ne tob̄\naiswests/ ka Wadschi muhſcham\nne taps iſwikſti/ un ka Wirwes\nne taps faraufſitas."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS buhs\npee numis augſt teizams/ ta\nbuhs weena Weeta/ kur Uppes\nun platti Stranti irr/ ka tur\nnekahda Laiwa ar Aireem ees/\nueds lahda zitta leela Laiwa\npahr to zelfees."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS irr\nmuhfu Teefatajs/ tas KUNGS\nirr muhſu Bauſlibas-Dewejs/\ntas KUNGS irr muhſu Keh-\nninsch/ wiꞥſch muhſ atpeſtihs."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lai tawas Wirwes tob̄\nusſtaipitas/ tomehr tahs to Ma-\nsta-Kohku ſtingri ne turrehs/ tee\narri to Wirs Karrogu ne isplat-\ntihs. Tad taps dands Laupi-\njuma iſdallibts/ ka arridsan tee\nTiſli to Laupijumu laupihs."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un neweens Eedſhwotajs\nfazzihs: Es etmu waifsch/ jo tee\nLandis/ kas eeſch ta dsihwo/dab-\nbuhs Peedohſchanu to Grehku."
    }
  ],
